        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Smart Sentencing Adjustments Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill establishes a grant program through which the Department of Justice may award grants to states to reduce the prison population of the state or to reduce the recurrence of recidivism after a term of incarceration and the collateral consequences experienced by individuals with criminal records. &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
